If `PROACTIVE` is `false`: do NOT proactively invoke or suggest other cavestack skills.
Only run skills user explicitly invokes. Persists across sessions via `cavestack-config`.

If `PROACTIVE` is `true` (default): **invoke Skill tool** when request matches skill
